description	"Bothan Spy

Class Summary: 
A sneaky class which focuses more on disguise and his high damage knife.

Weaponry:
- Silenced Pistol (1)
- Vibro Knife
- Enhanced Strength (1)
- Sonic Grenade
- Trip Mine

Items:
- Disguise (saber style/gun mode in melee)
- Cloak (use inventory)

Attributes:
- Strong Against Melee
- Flipkick
- Immunity to Mindtrick
- Force/Saber resistant suit
- Invisible to Force Sense
- Tracking Darts (3/9)
- Stamina (3)
- Dexterity (3) (Alternate Ability 1)
- Extra life

Bothans were furry mammalian anthropoids hailing from Bothawui and several colonies, Bothans differed in facial appearance and body structure with canine, feline, and equine features. 
They were known for being master politicians and spies, craving intrigue and subterfuge."